<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.5">
<l>maṟṟōr teyvameṇṇē ṉuṉṉaiyeṉ maṉattuvaittup</l>
<l>peṟṟēṉ peṟṟatuvum piṟavāmai yemperumāṉ</l>
<l>vaṟṟā nīḷkaṭalcū ḻilaṅkaiyi rāvaṇaṉaic</l>
<l>ceṟṟāy koṟṟavaṉē tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not think about any other god. Placing you in my heart,</l>
<l>I benefitted, and the benefit was birthlessness, my great lord,</l>
<l>You who killed Rāvaṇa of Laṅkā surrounded by the wide, inexhaustible sea,</l>
<l>Victorious one, [Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
